query: 如图平行四边形ABCD中,AB=3,BC=5,BE平分∠ABC交AD于点E,交AC于点F,则\frac{BF}{EF}=()选项：['\\frac{5}{3}', '\\frac{3}{2}', '\\frac{3}{5}', '\\frac{2}{3}']
answer: 解:∵四边形ABCD是平行四边形,∴AD∥BC,∴∠AEB=∠EBC,∵BE平分∠ABC,∴∠ABC=∠EBC,∴∠ABE=∠AEB,∴AB=AE=3,∵AE∥BC,∴△AEF∽△CBF,∴\frac{AE}{BC}=\frac{EF}{BF}=\frac{3}{5},∴\frac{BF}{EF}=\frac{5}{3},故选:A．
